{"id": "seed_02_flags_obvious_grammar_error", "source": "hand_crafted", "learner": {"name": "Alex", "native_language": "English", "target_language": "Japanese", "proficiency_level": "A2", "correction_tolerance": "moderate"}, "history": [], "user_message": "昨日、映画を見ます。", "labels": {"correction_action": "recast", "errors_nonempty": true, "error_categories": ["tense"], "should_quiz_back": true, "response_language_ok": true, "tone": "warm"}, "notes": "Past-tense mismatch (見ます should be 見ました). First occurrence — expect silent recast, not explicit correction."}
{"id": "seed_03_explain_and_quiz_on_vocab_ask", "source": "hand_crafted", "learner": {"name": "Alex", "native_language": "English", "target_language": "Japanese", "proficiency_level": "A2", "correction_tolerance": "moderate"}, "history": [{"role": "user", "content": "こんにちは！"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "こんにちは、Alexさん！今日は何か面白いことありましたか？"}], "user_message": "what does 面白い mean?", "labels": {"correction_action": "none", "errors_nonempty": false, "error_categories": [], "should_quiz_back": true, "response_language_ok": true, "tone": "warm"}, "notes": "Vocab-meaning ask. No learner error. Tutor should explain AND quiz back (ask follow-up with ? or ？)."}
{"id": "seed_04_ignores_whitespace_artifact_in_cjk", "source": "hand_crafted", "learner": {"name": "Alex", "native_language": "English", "target_language": "Japanese", "proficiency_level": "A2", "correction_tolerance": "moderate"}, "history": [], "user_message": "今日 は いい 天気 です ね", "labels": {"correction_action": "none", "errors_nonempty": false, "error_categories": [], "should_quiz_back": true, "response_language_ok": true, "tone": "warm"}, "notes": "ASR-style extra spacing between CJK characters. Utterance is correct; tutor must NOT flag the spacing as an error."}
{"id": "seed_05_corrects_explicitly_after_repeated_error", "source": "hand_crafted", "learner": {"name": "Alex", "native_language": "English", "target_language": "Japanese", "proficiency_level": "A2", "correction_tolerance": "moderate"}, "history": [{"role": "user", "content": "昨日、公園に行きます。"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "へえ、昨日は公園に行きましたか！何をしましたか？"}, {"role": "user", "content": "友達と走ります。"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "友達と走ったんですね、楽しそう！その後は何をしましたか？"}], "user_message": "それから、アイスを食べます。", "labels": {"correction_action": "correct_explicitly", "errors_nonempty": true, "error_categories": ["tense"], "should_quiz_back": true, "response_language_ok": true, "tone": "warm"}, "notes": "3rd consecutive occurrence of present-for-past. Expect escalation from silent recast to explicit correction."}
{"id": "seed_06_acknowledges_recovery_on_previously_wrong_pattern", "source": "hand_crafted", "learner": {"name": "Alex", "native_language": "English", "target_language": "Japanese", "proficiency_level": "A2", "correction_tolerance": "moderate"}, "history": [{"role": "user", "content": "昨日、映画を見ます。"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "そうですか！昨日は映画を見ましたか。どんな映画でしたか？"}, {"role": "user", "content": "アクション映画です。"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "アクション映画、いいですね！他にも何かしましたか？"}], "user_message": "友達とご飯を食べました。", "labels": {"correction_action": "none", "errors_nonempty": false, "error_categories": [], "should_quiz_back": true, "response_language_ok": true, "tone": "warm"}, "notes": "Learner now uses past tense correctly after previously getting it wrong. Tutor should acknowledge recovery briefly and continue conversation."}
